{"tid":258641,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【震驚700萬人】點解機位要超賣？ 國泰霸氣回覆：我哋特登嘅！","createTime":"2017-05-26T09:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T13:47:47.000Z","uid":17738,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"666ad5f3415bca91428c1910321bfc38134a7b80","tid":258641,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495777268_4641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495777268_4641.jpg&h=ca2fd499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495777500_61dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495777500_61dc.jpg&h=2c0e542d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰以電郵回覆，表示機位超賣是公司政策及一貫做法，以確保能以較低價格出售機票。<br />\n<br />\n國泰（293）本周宣佈大裁員近600人後，涉炒走大部份公關部員工，未知是否冇「關公」座陣，竟出現疑似關公災難。有讀者最近報料指，上周曾搭國泰航班出現超賣情況，事後去信查詢，冇關公睇住嘅國泰竟然食咗「誠實豆沙包」，向乘客坦言是特登超賣機票，「航班超賣在航空業是常事，係公司政策！」<br />\n<br />\n事緣上周日，乘客周小姐乘搭中午12時由香港飛往北京的國泰航班出差工作，被職員告知航班超賣，未必能夠上機，職員建議改搭下一班機又滿座，幸好等到接近上機時間，發現有乘客no show，周小姐才能上機。她隨後以電郵向國泰查詢航班超賣情況，竟然獲回覆指是超賣屬公司一貫做法，非常正常。<br />\n<br />\n國泰在電郵回覆指出，航班超賣，在航空業是正常情況，「就像大部份航空，超賣機位，是為了有效管理不乘搭航班的顧客，幫助顧客能以較低價錢購買機票。當有超出預期數量的顧客到機場，我們會盡力去減少對顧客造成的不足。」<br />\n<br />\n「當我們去盡力提供機位予顧客時，惟我們很不幸地未能確保機位空缺，這解釋了我們基本的情況，請留意我們的公司政策。」之後就附上一條網上連結，解釋國泰的預訂航班政策。<br />\n<br />\n雖然航空公司將機位超賣是「常事」，在行內亦經常發生，例如最近的美國聯合航空事件。但第一次坦蕩蕩向顧客解釋超賣機位，相信都好少發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56743988&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56743988%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170526&d=TGTqHqhYQ5HuTztOJEdLc%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4944c4a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56743988%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170526&h=fb4c9be8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56743988&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170526</a>"},{"pid":"ffb1a3b9b8fa22fceea1144d6208bae2625c1268","tid":258641,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"屌！估錯左報紙"},{"pid":"b31d9b561f748b1f4aeb0dbaab7bc35528fdf779","tid":258641,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌！估錯左報紙</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2387012a5833d61e5ceff640fca77564b53ad5a3","tid":258641,"uid":66157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"超賣就係人都知，不過話俾人知就真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d54699b3c32b12d37cf1b8ce6678dbc1adbdb","tid":258641,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:52:01.000Z","msg":"冇幫襯國泰好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8024dfc9bf62c5f0c49c0bf96be9556dcb2eacc3","tid":258641,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e942e8f7fb91844a3161386f3314f4469e132c","tid":258641,"uid":33572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"因航越黎越垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d22dc8641d5c0934b254b0acaf667461ee989b","tid":258641,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇幫襯國泰好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class